Text.Value: Bah!
Think me not a slave to mere nature: the children will be most beautiful.
*So you wander out alone to the rancid wastes, looking for the next creature who will accept your diseased embrace.*

EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: Dark Urge starts out walking upright, but as the next three narrator nodes go on and they get further into the darkness of the sewers, they get more and more crouched, like they've forgotten how to be a humanoid. ALTERNATIVE: they start to walk away, but as their urge drives them on, they begin to jog and then run, getting more excited and compelled

Text.Value: *Your memory of last night's act is absent. In the moment of mounting, your mind emptied itself, and you could think only of Bhaal.*
*Sire a new legion of Bhaalspawn, and set them upon self-slaughter. Your progeny must succeed where you fell.*
Pitter-patter!
New creatures will be grafted... such is the power of the Divine Essence.
Rah. Hrrhn. You mate well. Mate like will die soon.

EditorData.CinematicNodeContext: Worg waking up and turning around to the Dark Urge beside them.

Text.Value: *On your back in your septic nest, were you to encounter fifty a night, it would still not be enough.*
Father, I vow to thee: the call to coupling bewitches my loins, and I shall heed it.
I feel the burning within me. If you cannot fulfil it, I must depart to seek a new brood-partner.
Take pride, you may have bred a new Bhaalspawn.
Hnghhhh. Mmrhgh. Hee.
Scream.
GrrraAGGH.
NO! Again! And AGAIN!
*With your holy mission came the power to commune with the beasts.*
Quit stirring. Want sleep. Done with mate.
*Bhaal has use left for you. Following your failure, a new duty swelled within you:*
When will it end? When will it end?
*Bhaal demands the birth of a horde.*
Rrrrrh. Go. Or face claws.
Leave. Never see again. You not gnoll. Will not be litter.
Quiet. Tired.
*Thus you shall spend the rest of your days rutting, the lash of Father's disappointment the only thought in your rat's mind.*
*The gnoll's rump seemed to become his Temple's graven altar where you once led worship.*
My lust is not yet sated.
*Your lover sleeps yet.*
*As you awaken, your naked form aches with the exertions of coupling. Its effusions mingle with the cesspool around you.*

Text.Value: *What delights will you plumb next? Displacer beasts? Worgs? Carrion-crawlers?*
*The Urge has congealed in your mind and made of you a beast: a feral carcass with but a twitching knife-arm.*
